# Network Automation Lab

Personal lab for learning routing protocols and network automation.
Built with ContainerLab + Arista cEOS on Ubuntu.

## Lab 1 — OSPF 3-node topology
- R1: Area 0 internal router
- R2: ABR connecting Area 0 and Area 1
- R3: Area 1 internal router

## Tools
- ContainerLab, Arista cEOS 4.34.5M, Python 3 + Netmiko
EOF
